  <md:abstract><list>
<item>Define pitch.</item>
<item>Describe the relationship between the speed of sound, its frequency, and its wavelength.</item>
<item>Describe the effects on the speed of sound as it travels through various media.</item>
<item>Describe the effects of temperature on the speed of sound.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
